---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Shipping & Returns | PeptideResearch.eu">
  <section class="page-title bg-2">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
            <ul class="list-inline mb-0">
              <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="/" class="text-sm letter-spacing text-white text-uppercase font-weight-bold">Home</a></li>
              <li class="list-inline-item"><span class="text-white">|</span></li>
              <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="#" class="text-color text-uppercase text-sm letter-spacing">Shipping</a></li>
            </ul>
             <h1 class="text-lg text-white mt-2">Shipping & Returns</h1>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
          <h2 class="mb-3">Shipping Policy</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We ship to most countries within the European Union. All orders are dispatched from our EU warehouse.</p>
          <ul class="list-unstyled mb-5">
            <li class="mb-2"><i class="ti-check mr-2 text-color"></i><strong>Processing Time:</strong> Orders are typically processed within 1-2 business days.</li>
            <li class="mb-2"><i class="ti-check mr-2 text-color"></i><strong>Shipping Method:</strong> We use express couriers (DHL, FedEx, UPS) for all shipments.</li>
            <li class="mb-2"><i class="ti-check mr-2 text-color"></i><strong>Temperature Control:</strong> 
              <ul class="list-unstyled ml-4 mt-2">
                <li class="mb-1"><i class="ti-angle-right mr-2 text-color"></i><strong>Research Peptides:</strong> Lyophilized peptides are stable at ambient temperatures during transit.</li>
                <li class="mb-1"><i class="ti-angle-right mr-2 text-color"></i><strong>Skincare & Wellness:</strong> Most products are stable at room temperature. Temperature-sensitive items are shipped with cold packs.</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="mb-3">Return Policy</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Due to the nature of our products, we have specific return policies for each category:</p>
          
          <h3 class="h5 mb-3">Research Peptides</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">We generally do not accept returns of research chemicals to ensure the integrity of our supply chain. Once a product leaves our facility, we cannot guarantee its storage conditions.</p>

          <h3 class="h5 mb-3">Skincare & Wellness</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">Unopened skincare and wellness products may be returned within 14 days of delivery. Please contact support to initiate a return. Opened products cannot be returned for hygiene reasons.</p>

          <div class="alert alert-info border-0 shadow-sm" role="alert">
            <i class="ti-info-alt mr-2"></i>If you receive a damaged item or an incorrect product, please contact us within 48 hours of receipt, and we will arrange for a replacement.
          </div>

          <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3">Customs & Import Duties</h2>
          <p>For orders within the EU, there are no customs duties. For international orders, the customer is responsible for any import duties, taxes, or clearance fees.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
